# Personal Weekly Spending Analyzer

A data analytics project that analyzes
personal Weekly Spending patterns.

## Tools Used
- Python, Pandas, Matplotlib
- MySQL, Excel, Jupyter Notebook

## Key Results
- Total Spent: 3518
- Highest Day: Saturday (General Expenses)
- Lowest Day: Tuesday (Transport)

## Charts
- Bar Charts: Daily spending trend
- Pie Charts: Category breakdown
